==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Exeat
<hw>Ex"e*at</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L., let him go
forth.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A license for absence from a college or a
religious house.</def> <mark>[Eng.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shipley.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>A permission which a bishop grants to a priest to go
out of his diocese.</def> <rj><au>Wharton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Execrable</ent>⟦br⟧
